{"quotes": [{"lines": [{"text": "I was wondering why the people who would never dream of laughing at a blind or a crippled man would laugh at a moron?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Are there any questions? Did you enjoy the film?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Mr. Gordon... how do you feel at the present moment, about your development?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Grateful, sir.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "You are happy about it?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Yes.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Why?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Because it has allowed me to... see.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "To see what?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "The world.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "And what do you see in that world?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Well... my eyes are new, doctor, I...", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "And what do they *see*, Mr. Gordon?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Things as they are.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "And?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "And what they are becoming.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Can you give me an example Mr. Gordon?", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "[quickly]\nNo sir, you give me one.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Very well...", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Very well.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Modern science.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Rampant technology, conscience by computer.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Modern art.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Dispassionate draftsmen.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Foreign policy.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Brave new weapons.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[laughter]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Today's youth.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Joyless, guideless.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Today's religion.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Preachment by popularity polls.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Standard of living.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "A TV in every room.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[laughter]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Education.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "[agitated]\nA TV in every room.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[more laughter]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "The world's future, Mr. Gordon.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Brave new hates, brave new bombs, brave new wars.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "The coming generation.", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Test-tube conception, laboratory birth, TV education, brave new dreams, brave new hates, brave new wars; a beautifully purposeless process of society suicide.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[silence]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Any more questions?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Any more questions? In the back, any more questions about things as they are and what they're becoming? No? I have a question.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[turns to Nemur and Strauss]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Professor Nemur. Charly Gordon.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Nemur does not answer]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Come on, professor, you know. Charly Gordon.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Nemur still does not answer]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "You know, but you haven't told me.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[turns to the audience]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Anybody out there answer the question 'Charly Gordon'?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[no answer comes from the audience]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Anyone in the back answer the question 'Charly Gordon'?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[still no answer]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Charly Gordon is a fellow who will very shortly be what he used to be.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[the whole room is silent as Charly turns to Nemur and Strauss, puts his hand in his pocket and takes out Algernon who is now dead]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Professor Nemur, why didn't you tell me the success of the operation was only temporary?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Nemur and Strauss looked at each other in bewildered looks]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Marry me, pretty girl, marry me.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "We will marry at... quarter past Wednesday on the 74th of November, and our anniversary will happily be... on those days where we both remember.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "They say, Charly, that true love is letting go.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "What's enough love?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Always a little more than anyone ever gets.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[Charly picks up a book and reads from it]\n\"My name is Dick. I live in a house. I have a sister named Jane and a dog named Spot.\"", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[He throws the book away]\nMy name is Charly Gordon and I live in a room, and I got no sister and no dog, and I am stupid!", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "That, that is, is. That, that is not, is not. Is that it? It is.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Say, Miss Kinnian... where's Mr. Kinnian?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "He died, Charly.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[writes a sentence on the blackboard for Charly to punctuate]\nPunctuate it. Go ahead, punctuate it.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Charly does, and does it correctly]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "That's very good!", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "Now I have something for you to punctuate!", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Turns over blackboard where he has written a sentence]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "That does not make sense!", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Starts to punctuate it]\n'That that is", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[adds a comma]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": ", is", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[adds a period]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": ". That that is not", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[adds a comma]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": ", is not", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[adds a period]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": ".'", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Figures it out]\n'Is that it?'", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "'It is!'", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "So. Student surpasses the teacher!", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Charly nods eagerly]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[Alice slaps Charly on the face after been hardly kissed by him]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "You - you think anyone would ever want you, you stupid moron!", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Charly leaves Alice crying]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[Charly finds Alice waiting for him in his room]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Saw your cycle outside.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "It's for sale.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "What did you learn?", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "I'm back. What did you learn?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "I'm here.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Alice walks to him in a smile]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Any questions?", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[upset about getting fired from his job]\nYeah, I was wonder why people that would never dream of laughing at a blind or a crippled man would laugh at a moron.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "What happened?", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "My friends at the bakery got up a petition and then I got fired.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "Oh...", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "Is that an automatic law, something like gravity? Increased intelligence equals lost friends?", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[after witnessing Charly painting nude women, furiously at Richard]\nWhat are you trying to turn him into, some kind of a sideshow freak?", "character": "Dr. Anna Strauss", "characterId": "nm0803785"}, {"text": "Now, Anna, don't be ridiculous.", "character": "Dr. Richard Nemur", "characterId": "nm0417824"}, {"text": "You're pushing your program for his intellectual development much too rapidly. It has to keep pace with my program for his emotional development, or the imbalance will become dangerous! I thought we were to be satisfied with a minor miracle...", "character": "Dr. Anna Strauss", "characterId": "nm0803785"}, {"text": "What are you afraid of?", "character": "Dr. Richard Nemur", "characterId": "nm0417824"}, {"text": "...to help a retarded human being become a more productive member of society.", "character": "Dr. Anna Strauss", "characterId": "nm0803785"}, {"text": "He has shown no indication of any mental ceiling. So why are you afraid to reach for whatever that ceiling may be? In any event, we shall have to give Mrs. Kinnian her notice.", "character": "Dr. Richard Nemur", "characterId": "nm0417824"}, {"text": "What?", "character": "Dr. Anna Strauss", "characterId": "nm0803785"}, {"text": "All she can do now is ask him questions out of books that he's already absorbed. What he needs at this point is a giant step forward - new conceptualization, inductive thinking. And that calls for experts, not Alice Kinnian.", "character": "Dr. Richard Nemur", "characterId": "nm0417824"}, {"text": "Charly Gordon is still a child emotionally.", "character": "Dr. Anna Strauss", "characterId": "nm0803785"}, {"text": "I don't agree.", "character": "Dr. Richard Nemur", "characterId": "nm0417824"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[last lines]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Marry me?", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Charly goes silent by refusing]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "[sits down]\nAll right, don't marry me.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[smiles]\nMotion carried.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "But I'm going to stay right here. Whenever you feel like telling me to go, just let me know - just tell me so. I'll go, I'll leave.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "Leave.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Alice goes stunned]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Please, leave.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[solemnly]\nAll right...", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[Alice hesitates then slowly heads to the door]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Good night.", "character": "Alice Kinnian", "characterId": "nm0001954"}, {"text": "[without looking at her]\nGood night.", "character": "Charly Gordon", "characterId": "nm0731772"}, {"text": "[Alice leaves]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "00. There'll be no hokey-pokey in my house!", "character": "Mrs. Apple", "characterId": "nm0925418"}]}]}